<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 02:36:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>F-35 在内华达州试验和训练场坠毁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/f-35-crashes-in-the-nevada-test-and-training-range-complex</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天早些时候，这架飞机在拉斯维加斯北部的综合靶场坠毁，飞行员安全弹射逃生。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/f-35-crashes-in-the-nevada-test-and-training-range-complex"&gt;F-35 在内华达测试和训练场坠毁后（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 23:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/f-35-crashes-in-the-nevada-test-and-training-range-complex</guid></item><item><title>新型 EA-37B 罗盘号电子战喷气机将跨大西洋、中东？ （更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ea-37b-compass-call-electronic-attack-jets-cross-the-pond-middle-east-next</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些喷气式飞机可以为中央司令部提供美国最先进的防区外干扰能力，包括中断通信和防空。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ea-37b-compass-call-electronic-attack-jets-cross-the-pond-middle-east-next"&gt;新型 EA-37B 指南针号召电子战喷气机跨大西洋，下一个是中东？ （已更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 22:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ea-37b-compass-call-electronic-attack-jets-cross-the-pond-middle-east-next</guid></item><item><title>美国中东基地掩体现在是五角大楼的首要任务</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunkers-for-u-s-bases-in-middle-east-now-a-top-priority</link><description>&lt;p&gt;急于加强中东基地的行动最终应该为全球范围内的巨大差距敲响急需的警钟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunkers-for-u-s-bases-in-middle-east-now-a-top-priority"&gt;《中东美国基地的掩体现在是五角大楼的首要任务》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 19:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunkers-for-u-s-bases-in-middle-east-now-a-top-priority</guid></item><item><title>前 KC-135 联队指挥官谈如何推动对抗中国</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/what-it-will-take-to-fuel-a-fight-against-china-from-former-kc-135-wing-commander</link><description>&lt;p&gt;退役空军上校特洛伊·帕纳农 (Troy Pananon) 坦率地阐述了与中国的战斗会给加油机舰队带来的压力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/what-it-will-take-to-fuel-a-fight-against-china-from-former-kc-135-wing-commander"&gt;前 KC-135 联队指挥官论如何推动对抗中国的斗争&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 18:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/what-it-will-take-to-fuel-a-fight-against-china-from-former-kc-135-wing-commander</guid></item><item><title>莱茵金属与波音联手，MQ-28“幽灵蝙蝠”在欧洲获得主要立足点</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-gains-major-european-foothold-as-rheinmetal-joins-forces-with-boeing</link><description>&lt;p&gt;MQ-28 Ghost Bat 可以由德国空军部署，但潜在利润丰厚的欧洲 CCA 市场也敞开大门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-gains-major-european-foothold-as-rheinmetal-joins-forces-with-boeing"&gt;随着莱茵金属公司与波音公司联手，MQ-28 后的“幽灵蝙蝠”在欧洲获得了主要立足点&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 18:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-gains-major-european-foothold-as-rheinmetal-joins-forces-with-boeing</guid></item><item><title>数十架 A-10 疣猪似乎准备加入 Epic Fury</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在部署更多疣猪之际，越来越多的迹象表明伊朗领土上的地面行动可能很快就会发生。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury"&gt;数十架 A-10 疣猪似乎准备加入史诗之怒的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 22:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰使用私人防空队保护工业免受俄罗斯无人机的攻击</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰希望通过动员私营部门来减轻其部队的防空负担，同时扩大覆盖范围。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones"&gt;乌克兰使用私人防空队保护工业免受俄罗斯无人机攻击的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 20:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones</guid></item><item><title>A-10 疣猪机在伊拉克进行奇怪的长时间扫射</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq</link><description>&lt;p&gt;A-10 进行九秒长的射击绝对不正常。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq"&gt;A-10 疣猪在伊拉克进行奇怪的长时间扫射&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq</guid></item><item><title>以色列 F-16 战机似乎携带集束弹药</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些集束弹药可能有一个非常特殊的目的，旨在削弱伊朗发射远程弹道导弹的能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions"&gt;以色列 F-16 战机似乎携带集束弹药&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions</guid></item><item><title>图片显示 E-3 哨兵在伊朗袭击中被完全摧毁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike</link><description>&lt;p&gt;失去一架 E-3 对于机身日益摇摇欲坠的日益萎缩的机队来说是一个重大打击，并表明了其他能力和防御方面的差距。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike"&gt;图片显示 E-3 哨兵在伊朗袭击中被完全摧毁（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 17:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike</guid></item></channel></rss>